headline: Teledyne Brown Engineering Secures $42.9 Million NAVSEA Contract Modification to Sustain MK11 SEAL Delivery Vehicle Fleet
summary: HUNTSVILLE, Ala., December 09, 2025--Teledyne Brown Engineering, Inc., a subsidiary of Teledyne Technologies Incorporated (NYSE:TDY) and a leader in advanced engineering and manufacturing solutions, announced it has received a $42,882,299 firm-fixed-price contract modification from the Naval Sea Systems Command (NAVSEA) to provide Provisioned Items Order spares in support of the MK11 SEAL Delivery Vehicle (SDV) program.
